Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\\4aFF\pos(473.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:11.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:15.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:23.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(490.117,670.389)}Fossil Man Hitodanger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen closely,\Nall you young ladies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go falling\Nfor a mountain man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he gets lost in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll end up a young widow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he gets lost in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll end up a young widow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're almost there. \NHow are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:01:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get to the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll report to the others at\Nthe base through the transceiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll join you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you just slipped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Bro! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like starfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.\NStarfish live in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep going that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy,\Nyou've got weird interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you it's\Nsome secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaru, you read too much manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a picture of me with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NA little further back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:03:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a good one, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a starfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Snow and rocks will be our home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not cut out for the city
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're just not cut\Nout for the city
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, do you know how\Nmuch water we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NI've done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure?\NI can't stand undercooked rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching a fish for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobei here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Hiromi here. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might be\Nfeeling lonely. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato and Taki haven't dropped\Nby, so I'm all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I hadn't caught\Nthis stupid cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so boring. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I read you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring back a souvenir,\Nso just wait for us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Interference from something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi here! Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next to Tengu Rock...\Na starfish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A starfish monster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Can you hear me? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy said he saw\Na starfish monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tengu Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaru! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you hurt my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything\Nwithout my glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a mountain a boy\Nshould be climbing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A starfish monster took my\Nbrother into some weird building.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A starfish monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the town at the foot of\Nthe mountain, then look for your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be a\Nstrange question,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but does Foggy Peak have\Nany connection to starfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, most certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They found a starfish fossil\Nthat was just enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A fossil, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That means this whole area used\Nto be under the ocean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But they say it was alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.39,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,But it's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:26.22,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Starfish are hardy animals that\Ncan even regrow their own limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Where is this fossil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact,\Nit's gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We all ran around searching,\Nthinking it'd run away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:40.57,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Shocker must have stolen it\Nand turned it into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plans for world\Ndomination are proceeding smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the underground missile base\Nhere on Foggy Peak is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will cause widespread\Ndestruction and take over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitodanger, remain alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this base can use its missiles\Nto sow destruction across the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you must not let a\Nsingle person approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture anyone who gets\Nnear, and execute them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are inhuman!\NYou monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure do love the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh air, clean water...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something\Nto that building...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've traced the mystery\Nradio waves that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI headquarters picked\Nup back to this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it's connected to\Nthe recent disappearances
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of local mountain-climbers,\Ntoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shown yourselves, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider,\Nthis thing's body is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The body of Hitodanger,\Nhardened over tens of thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was stronger than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:30.21,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(331,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider should have left a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Search the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I came running because I\Nthought I heard you down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were one of\Nthat starfish monster's gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a strange\Nmessage on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was talking about a starfish\Nmonster, so I came to check it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If our favorite FBI\Nagent is snooping around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that means Shocker's\Ninvolved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredibly powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It knocked Kamen\NRider for a loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider? That's not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't head out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still\Nsearching the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they haven't caught Rider yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If he went to Tengu Rock...\Nthat's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,\Nhe's been gone way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He could have fallen\Ninto a crevasse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! It's not a telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the camp for the\NTachibana Racing Club. Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down!\NC'mon, let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.55,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,It's Tobei and Taki here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Taki is with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:30.92,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:32.19,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Has Hayato been down your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato hasn't been by! Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.91,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:39.91,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,But all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where Rider was beaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't beat me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay in there\Nuntil we find Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At least take off the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they bring you in, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll untie you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Their cruelty is unspeakable...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a\Nmonster they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, look alive, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work together\Nas mountain men
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and find a way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really worried\Nabout my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you open it with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's going to regret\Ncatching this mountain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just unlocking the door\Nwon't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Security is too tight to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Get into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But what good will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\NI think I'm good in a brawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you! That really hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quiet down, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?\NI said quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to\Npipe down or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid little...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem a bit old for\Na Shocker combatant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll disconnect the alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all\Nright on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll flick the lights three\Ntimes to show it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I do, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...\Nthis would be the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you people doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're imposters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Acetylene, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what to do with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... they've found us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire! There's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, we can't go out\Ndressed like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound the alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't put it out quickly,\Nthe building will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!\NDon't get it on me, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,He seems afraid of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:17.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,Absorption of water will\Nrestore the fossil to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lead you all to your doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get in there! \N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't beat me this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitodanger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body will have\Nabsorbed that water,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,making you soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:21.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato, the Kamen Rider,\Nhad defeated the fossil monster Hitodanger
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:24.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and foiled Shocker's\Nevil schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:29.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The fight only made him more determined\Nto fight Shocker and protect the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.88,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,560)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(490.031,476.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:44.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:45.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Crab Bubbler.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:48.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A series of mysterious\Ntsunamis on the Pacific Coast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:50.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,leads the gang to Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:53.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The fight between our brave\NKamen Rider and Crab Bubbler
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:56.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,unfolds amidst the\Nbounties of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:24:00.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Monstrous\NCrab Bubbler Appears in Hokkaido."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:24:00.89,Static Texts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\fscx100\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(493.714,208.5)}The Monstrous Crab Bubbler
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:24:00.89,Static Texts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\fscx100\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(522.738,648.451)}Appears in Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:11.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:13.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:15.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:18.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:22.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:24.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:25.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:28.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.53,0:24:34.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:37.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.79,0:24:41.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.87,0:24:45.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!